    "body": "This is a *very* specific feature and I am not sure if we should really put more abstraction into the bindings in order to support it. The BoundContract already contains almost only interfaces. I'm pretty sure you can just implement your logic as a `ContractTransactor` and set that in the `BoundContract` for all bindings. You could also patch all your generated bindings to use your `ContractTransactor` in their `bindContractName` method.",
